{"tid":328532,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"食支煙又有罪咩？","createTime":"2017-07-19T15:55:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-19T16:17:33.000Z","uid":94075,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8aa9aff0bf65ed2bfdee626d91a0299b38cdae93","tid":328532,"uid":94075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T15:55:24.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 本身都唔太喜歡食煙嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平時見到啲煙剷係有蓋地方食煙都會兇鳩佢地搵控煙辦 <br />\n仲有啲會一路行一路食煙嘅更加痴撚線 要啲路人吸撚埋啲二手煙<br />\n但真係高處未算高<br />\n屌你老味 今日去商場個陣係停車場等𨋢 <br />\n一打開門有個阿叔係度煲煙<br />\n仆你個街即刻忍唔住講句喂有冇搞錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n痴撚線搞到架𨋢臭到 成陣煙味<br />\n你班死煙剷自己想生肺癌就算 咪撚累鳩其他人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我真係好撚嬲所以會講到1999"},{"pid":"05907f24e72cfbadec24c9bf7bd458149024c18f","tid":328532,"uid":24264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T16:06:44.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"0a84aa7f5ef731f42743e37d212b5c546ba65018","tid":328532,"uid":125773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T16:17:22.000Z","msg":"題搵不符"},{"pid":"8405258df284f9a2d51d9554b5529e830fef8814","tid":328532,"uid":125773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T16:17:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>題搵不符</blockquote><br />\n文"}]}